divs: Sighting DetailsSITING ON THE BALCONY ON THE HILL ONE HOT SUMMER GETING SOME FRESH AIR I NOTICED SOMETHING STRANGE IN THE SKY. IT DIDN'T LOOK LIKE A AIRPLAIN IT DIDN'T HAVE ANY WINGS. THE SPACE SHIP WAS DISC SILVER SHAPED IT WAS DARK COULD SEE THE SHINNING SILVER. THE THING I NOTICED THERE WAS THREE GREEN CIRCLED LIGHTS ARE IN THE SPACE SHIP.THE ONE IN THE MIDDLE WAS GOING SIDE BY SIDE AND IT THE SPACE SHIP WITH THE THREE GREEN LIGHTS WAS COMING TOWARDS ME AND THE CITY!
